  "texts": [
    "These developments underscore AI's growing role in value creation within the discipline.",
    "While some argue that the era of theory-building is over (Anderson, 2008; Rheinberger, 2023), others suggest its role is evolving (Spinney, 2022), and many continue to defend its necessity (Pigliucci, 2008; Popper, 1959; Simanowski, 2016).",
    "It must be noted that AI is not naturally curious (Kissinger et al., 2022).",
    "Despite AI's achievements, including the Nobel Prize winning AlphaFold, answering the \"why\" questions, especially from patient-centered and culturally sensitive perspectives, it still requires human insight.",
    "Until datasets encompass the full breadth of human knowledge and experience, theorizing and empirical testing will remain essential."
